OL,5, Roman Kemp has said hosting the Capital
OL,6, breakfast show over the past four years
OL,7, was like reliving the "horrible day" of
OL,8, the death of his friend and producer   
OL,9, "over and over again".                 
OL,11,FKemp was in the middle of an edition of
OL,12,Fhis radio show in August 2020 when he  
OL,13,Ffound out Joe Lyons had killed himself.
OL,15,F"I went through such a horrible moment 
OL,16,Fin that room, in that studio," he said.
OL,18,F"Four years on and I've been living    
OL,19,Fthat same day over and over again,     
OL,20,Fwithout the awful event."              
